how to run app:

1. cd backend
2. python -m venv venv
3. source venv/bin/activate
4. pip install -r requirements.txt
5. python run.py

frontend:
1. copy paste this url into your browser: http://127.0.0.1:5000/

endpoints:
http://127.0.0.1:5000 - base url
/api/data - returns a unified json of all the data
/api/data/<string:file_type> - returns a unified json of all the files of the specified file type

backend: python, python flask
frontend: html, vanilla css, vanilla js, python flask render

how to use the app:
# uploading files
1. choose files to upload
2. click upload
# unifying data
3. select the file type to unify by [csv/json/pdf/pptx]
4. click unify
5. click the "Jump to Data" button to jump to the unified data
# visualizing data
6. select a visualization option [table/tree]
7. click visualize